    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Self-Sufficiency (period)",
      "description": "**Self-Sufficiency** answers: *how much of what I consumed did I produce myself?*\n\nFormula: `(1 − grid_import / consumption) × 100`\n\nA high value means you relied little on the grid — your solar panels covered most of your needs.",
